doctype html
html(lang="en")
  head
    include header

    title Remembrall – FAQ
  body
    section.faq
      h1 How it works
  
      p Send messages to 
        a(href='https://t.me/remembrall_robot') @remembrall_robot 
        | in Telegram: paste your 
        strong links
        | , add descriptions and 
        strong #tags
        | .

      h3 Where can I find a list of all commands?

      ul
        li 
          strong /getlink
          |  — get a link to your Remembrall page; only you can see it.
        li 
          strong /makepublic
          |  — make Remembrall page visible for everyone on the internet.
        li 
          strong /makeprivate
          |  — make Remembrall page available only with the secret key.
        li 
          strong /resetkey 
          |  — reset Remembrall link secret token.
        li 
          strong /forget 
          |  — delete message from database.

      h3 How many links I can store up with Remembrall?
      p Remembrall has a storage limit: every user can store up 
        strong 250 messages
        | . When you go over the storage limit, you can still read existing content, but you won't be able to add new links. However, you can delete existing messages to free up your storage.

      h3 How do I edit message?
      p Just edit it in Telegram conversation.

      h3 How I can delete my message?
      p If you want to remove information from your Remembrall page, open chat with Remembrall bot, find the message and reply on it with 
        strong /forget
        |  command. In situation when message has already been deleted from conversation, you can get link on it. 
        br
        | Copy link on Remembrall page by tapping # icon and send it to 
        a(href='https://t.me/remembrall_robot') @remembrall_robot
        |  with 
        strong /forget
        |  command.

      h3 What happens if I change my username on Telegram?
      p If you want to update your url on Remembrall page, you should enter 
        strong /fixname
        |  command.

      h3 Which content I can save with Remembrall?
      p Now you can store up only text and links. If you need more, message me.

      h3 Can I use Remembrall in groups and channels?
      p No. Bot stores up messages only by regular users.

      h3 I still have questions. Who can I ask them?
      p If you have any further questions, comments and suggestion, 
        a(href='https://github.com/antonlukin/remembrall/issues/new') open new ticket
        |  on Github or write me to 
        a(href='https://t.me/lukin') Telegram
        |  directly.
  
